{"word":"Shoe","slug":"shoe","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shoe</b> Taken off on holy ground<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=5'>Exo 3:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=15'>Jos 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=33'>Act 7:33</a><br/> Put off in mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=17'>Eze 24:17</a><br/> Shoes of the children of Israel did not wax old<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=5'>Deu 29:5</a><br/> Loosed in token of refusal to observe the Levirate marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=9'>Deu 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=8'>Rth 4:8</a><br/> Poor sold for a pair of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=2&verse=6'>Amo 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=8&verse=6'>Amo 8:6</a><br/> Made of iron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=25'>Deu 33:25</a><br/> Made of badgers' skins<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=10'>Eze 16:10</a><br/> Latchet of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=23'>Gen 14:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=27'>Isa 5:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=7'>Mar 1:7</a><br/> Loosing of, a humble service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=16'>Luk 3:16</a>"}]}